features: Full HD Picture Perfection - Full HD Picture Perfection gives you crystal-clear, award-winning picture quality. Contrast and brightness are achieved with Full Array LED Backlight and fine-tuned at a granular level with Active Pixel Tuning.

America’s Smart TV - Instantly access millions of titles with America's Smart TV. Stream shows, movies, news, sports, music, and more on all your favorite apps, and enjoy over 250 free channels on WatchFree+.

Free TV Lives Here - Save on cable bills and stream for free with VIZIO WatchFree+. Built-in to every new VIZIO TV, WatchFree+ gives you 250+ live streaming channels and over 5,000 titles on demand. No subscriptions, logins, or fees.

Powerful Performance - The VIZIO D-Series has the horsepower for powerful performance. Superior picture processing, ultra-quick app navigation and reduced load times are powered by the IQ Picture Processor.
Gaming Amplified - Great gaming that's ready for next-gen consoles and PCs.
body.description: This pre-owned or refurbished product has been professionally inspected and tested to work and look like new. How a product becomes part of Amazon Renewed, your destination for pre-owned, refurbished products: A customer buys a new product and returns it or trades it in for a newer or different model. That product is inspected and tested to work and look like new by Amazon-qualified suppliers. Then, the product is sold as an Amazon Renewed product on Amazon. If not satisfied with the purchase, renewed products are eligible for replacement or refund under the Amazon Renewed Guarantee.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Very cheap, tv mount came with wrong hardware, no instructions or manual for tv our mount
reviews.reviewText: The included TV mount is very cheap. The hardware it came with does not even fit the Vesa mount holes on the TV, I had to go to the hardware store and get my own screws/hardware. There were no instructions for the mount, no manual for the TV, and the product is just very cheap quality overall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars TV barely survived 100 days.
reviews.reviewText: I didn’t mind the slowness and lag of this TV at first, but it gradually got worse with time. Now on its 95th day the whole TV went blank and unusable. Vizio Support was awful and incompetent and dragged my case around until there was no conclusion. Not worth the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great picture and menu
reviews.reviewText: I wanted something small for my bedroom that I could connect my headphones to and this fit the bill. After research, I found ROKU doesn’t have a way to connect the headphones so “heads up”. I’m really happy with this tv. Many capabilities and venues. You won’t be sorry! Easy to set up as well.

Es muy buen producto, yo la uso la mayor parte del tiempo como monitor y tienes una calidad excelente, muy buen definición. Como television si deja que desear, ya que el smarcast no esta disponible en mexico, osea que solo puedes usar estreaming si el control tiene accesos directos (botones) pero el chrome cast integrado de la tele sirve muy bien para proyectar desde tu celular o tablet.
